com.sterlingcommerce.woodstock.callout

Class SCCountingVotingResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.woodstock.callout.SCCountingVotingResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISCVotingResolver

    public class SCCountingVotingResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISCVotingResolver
    This voting resolver will proceed if the execution of a unit is successful or not. It continues to next call out unit if any unit times out or results in exception. Suspends the unit if its times out or any exeception is encountered Skips any suspended unit within the call out chain
